    "body": "This PR\r\n* add `S` to toggle recording states; cc https://github.com/KMiri-rs/miri/pull/3\r\n  * on demand: continue, count forward steps, or steps in run-to-terminator  won't be recorded\r\n  * always (default): any execution forward will be recorded\r\n* supports count forward and back step in reverse mode",
